                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Chargé <persName type="from">Eddy</persName> to the <gloss
                            type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Embassy</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">St. Petersburg</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1905-11-02">
                            <hi rend="italic">November 2, 1905</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(Mr. Eddy reports that according to a proclamation just issued the departments of
                    the army, navy, and the imperial domain will not come under the jurisdiction of
                    the new parliament. Under another proclamation all political prisoners not
                    deemed dangerous to the state will be released. Reports of the gravest character
                    have been received from Odessa.)</p>
            </div>
        </body>
